719284f-a.text:
Delancey Street, north side, west from Clinton to Norfolk Streets. Loew's Delancey Theatre, is at the N.W. corner of Suffolk Street.
February 12, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
The 6-story structure partially shown on the right.is to be replaced by a 1-story business building according to the Times of May 3, 1938. This bears Nos. 156-164 Delancey Street and No. 107Clinton Street; being
at the N.W. corner of same.
